root: ^Welcome to your first day at The Astro Parcel Service. To save time, team members call it TAPS.
^I'm your manager. You can refer to me as Manager. I don't care who you are. You'll be zipping around in this job so I'm just going to call you Zip.
^At TAPS, we deliver packages containing plants and high quality customer service.
^But we can't do that with you just standing around! Get to work, Zip!
